When a sale order line billed on delivered timesheets has been invoiced,
Odoo forbids modification of the unit price. When a price update is
necessary, one can create a new sale order or sale order line, but it is
painful to link all projects, tasks, milestones to the new order line.

This modules adds a button on already invoiced timesheet sale order
lines to update the unit price. It creates a new order line with the new
price and re-links projects, tasks, milestones and so line employee maps
from the old line to the new line.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Usage
=====

There is a button with a banknote icon on the sale order line. When
clicked, it opens a wizard to update the unit price of the sale order
line.

